price: 93. Alle sokadi? Miyey idiin gargaari karaan,mase u gargaari karaan nafahooda?
arabic: مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ هَلۡ يَنصُرُونَكُمۡ أَوۡ يَنتَصِرُونَ

version.title: Somali translation - Jacob
